ain, FREE NOVEMBER will be subjected to an official veterinary examination.\nA veterinary inspection of SUGAR immediately following the race including an endoscopic examination showed a substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea.  Before being allowed to race again, SUGAR will be subjected to an official veterinary examination.\nDANE PATROL and COUNTRY MELODY were sent for sampling.", "DeclarHorseWt": 1011}
