E HAPPIEST shifted ground outwards when being ridden out.\nFor the majority of the race, both LUCKY DAN and MEDIC SWORDSMAN travelled wide and without cover.\nCHARITY KINGDOM and UNIQUE HAPPIEST were sent for sampling.", "DeclarHorseWt": 1155, "Sec4DBL": 10.5}
